content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

Prepare to get very sad, Outlander viewers.

We won’t give away specific details about Outlander Season 2 Episode 10 right now, but a major character was killed off during the hour.

It focused on Jamie using Claire’s knowledge about the future to lead the Jacobite army into battle against the British, while Claire herself tended to the wounded.

This served as harsh reminder of the cost of war

What else went down during the episode? Who died? We’ve got the answers to all these questions and more.

Just use the above video to watch Outlander online and find out now!
